  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    As an aid to IT architects and designers, an AD Summary Report may be produced from the AD repository. This report&#xD;
    lists all the ADs related to the topic or area of interest.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The AD Summary has an overall title based upon the query, or specified manually by the requester. Also, for each AD,&#xD;
    the title,&amp;nbsp;reference number, and the date of approval is included in following structure (one for each included&#xD;
    AD):&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    &amp;lt;Report Title&amp;gt;&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;blockquote style=&quot;MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>&#xD;
    &lt;h4>&#xD;
        &amp;lt;Architectural Decision Title&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/h4>&#xD;
    &lt;h5>&#xD;
        Reference:&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;reference number&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;lt;date&amp;gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/h5>&#xD;
    &lt;h5>&#xD;
        Decision&#xD;
    &lt;/h5>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        &amp;lt;text&amp;gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        The Reference number line is followed by a direct extract of the &quot;&lt;strong>Decision&lt;/strong>&quot; sub-section in the&#xD;
        referenced AD.&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>&#xD;
        Optionally the following section of the Architectural Decision is included for each AD:&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;/blockquote>&#xD;
&lt;blockquote>&#xD;
    &lt;h5>&#xD;
        Impacts and Implications&#xD;
    &lt;/h5>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        &amp;lt;text&amp;gt;&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
    &lt;p>&#xD;
        This is a direct extract of the section of the same name in the defined AD. It documents any implications of the&#xD;
        decision, such as technology choice, cost, and support implications. It also documents and cross-references any&#xD;
        implications on other ADs, past or present.&#xD;
    &lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;/blockquote>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    A template has been defined for this report: &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithType&quot;&#xD;
    href=&quot;./../../../UAM/guidances/templates/uam_ad_summary_E8ECFBD8.html&quot; guid=&quot;_691yINWpEdyLINQdtlJihw&quot;>Template:&#xD;
    Architectural Decisions Summary Template&lt;/a>.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
